Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.96,0:00:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{=2}Yes, everything in the report is accurate. \NIt was entirely our fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.97,0:00:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! In one week?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not at all. \NPlease leave it to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.96,0:00:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, are you planning on \Nfighting the Abydos kids again?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But we already blew all our cash. \NWhat do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.94,0:00:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're bound to run short\N on funds renting this fancy office {TM: check leadin}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.46,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a company without a proper office?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.93,0:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'd be fine with  pitching tents in the park like last time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.50,0:00:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I would also be fine anywhere \Nas long as you're there, Miss Aru...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.28,0:00:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you all just be quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.66,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take out a loan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.47,0:00:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But aren't you blacklisted from the banks?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.29,0:00:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been declared a public enemy and had my assets frozen, that's all!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.36,0:01:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! I'm not letting this mission end like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.30,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for choosing Kaiser Loan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.51,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have confirmed the receipt of \N 788 million, 3 thousand 250 yen, in cash. {TM: Might split, come back to this}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.89,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you again next month.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.46,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we managed to scrape by this month.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.56,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I wonder why Kaiser Loan\N only accepts cash for the payments?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.83,0:03:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. It would be much easier to simply transfer the amount from a bank account.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.60,0:03:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No attacking the transport car, Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that. {TM: Check}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's begin our regular meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.74,0:03:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, about the part \Nthat we recovered the other day. {TM: Might snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.05,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out that this part did in fact originate from the Black Market. 
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.09,0:03:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous place that deals in many illegal items
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.99,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and is notorious as a hotbed for unauthorized clubs.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.06,0:03:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that Problem Solver 68 \N are often spotted visiting the area as well. {TM: fade this in}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.82,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.03,0:03:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like they were after our school, same as the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.95,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With how often we've been attacked, there's gotta be something else going on that we don't know about.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it could be.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.29,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigating the connection between these events might lead us to finding out the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.84,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guess that settles it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little field trip, shall we?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.47,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got some new firearms in stock.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, for real?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.06,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so wild.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Black Market
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the people!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.74,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the holes in the GSC's network\N have gotten this big.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're always cooped up \N the Abydos area. {should that be district? --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's full of strange places like these.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been here before, Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, this is my first time, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.98,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there are plenty of wacky things out in the other school districts. 
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.94,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this one place has giant aquariums. \NI hear they're huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go one of these days. {TM: Check if should snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... that sounds nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, there's no telling \N what could happen out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Comment: 10,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hifumi noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I said quit running!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop following me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's have some fun!
Comment: 10,0:04:57.74,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's all the same to you, I'd really rather not... {TM: with the cry}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.24,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's all the same to you, I'd really rather not... {TM: without}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Her uniform is from Trinity?!
Comment: 10,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hifumi noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, uh, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.13,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?\NBack off, it's her that we want!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.63,0:05:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's from Trinity General School, \N the richest school in Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.64,0:05:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna borrow her for a bit\Nand ask for a little money in return, see!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.21,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch and release.\NPretty slick, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say? \N Want in on this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split the ransom -
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call. {TM: Might snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ajitani Hifumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi, huh. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, what's a girl from Trinity doing\N in such a rough part of town?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually looking for something. {TM: might snap but probably not?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any stores that sell it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard that it's secretly \Nbeing traded around here still.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you talking about a tank?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Illegal firearms, perhaps?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, maybe biochemical weapons?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.23,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, nothing like that. It's, uhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,limited-edition Mister Peroro merch. {Check global for how Peroro was handled! --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.11,0:06:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Peroro?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this guy right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.78,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Mister Peroro plush that had a very limited run. \NOnly 100 units were ever produced. {TM: Probably want to split this but ugh}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.49,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's from Momo Friends! \NI'm a huge fan, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Peroro's so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! {TM: Check snap?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.29,0:06:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, the times have sure moved on, haven't they.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what are all of you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're also looking for something.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.68,0:06:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you can find easily,\N but we heard that it would be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NGuess we're kind of in the same boat, huh. {TM: Check snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.85,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, looks like your shopping trip took quite the nasty turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.04,0:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, I knew this place was bad news before.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.35,0:07:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd also heard that the corporations were taking advantage of the GSC's absence to run wild here...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.85,0:07:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apparently gotten so bad that it has \Nits own bank and security force.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.54,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, those would also fall under unauthorized, illegal operations, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.75,0:07:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the security forces \N here are especially bad news.{TM: Check snap}
Comment: 10,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Hifumi, you sure know your stuff. {TM: version with the "wow", if used prev line needs to be adjusted}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Hifumi, you sure know your stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's settled, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.31,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We helped you out, now it's your turn to help us with what we're looking for!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we want \N a loan from these guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This bank is part of the Black Market.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The interest rates must be h-horrible...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.49,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be fair, we don't even know if\N Aru will pass the background check.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quiet, you. Of course I'll pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.02,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd. There should be at least some\N information on your illegal part, but I can't find any.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The purchase history, storage records...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's gone to the effort of hiding all of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the feeling I'm getting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone doesn't want us to find it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.26,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. The corporations may run this place, but \N even they shouldn't be able to do all this...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't normal?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, why bother going that far?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.24,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The corporations here are almost flaunting their illegal activities at this point,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.31,0:08:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so it seems odd that they would try to hide anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that building, for example. {TM: might snap? Probs not.}
Comment: 10,0:08:38.42,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even within the Black Market, that bank is notorious for its shady business. {TM: Combined ver}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even within the Black Market,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.53,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that bank is notorious for its shady business.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shady?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've heard,
Comment: 10,0:08:46.42,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,nearly 15 percent of all the money that funds criminal activity in Kivotos is being funneled straight into that bank. {TM: Combined version for posterity}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,nearly 15 percent of all the money that funds criminal activity in Kivotos
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is being funneled straight into that bank.
Comment: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hoshino noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.03,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Money that is obtained from various crimes like embezzlement, theft, and kidnapping
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.86,0:09:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,are then turned into weapons and equipment to be used in other crimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vicious cycle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.03,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, but doesn't that mean the bank \N is basically assisting those crimes?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.78,0:09:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Even the banks here are criminal organizations. {TM: Unsplit}
Comment: 10,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Comment: 10,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the Market Guard! {TM: Split ver}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.44,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Market Guard!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Market Guard?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.90,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the top of the top within the security forces here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're escorting that vehicle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a cash transport.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who always collects \Nour money for the bank?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.11,0:09:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patience.\NHere is this month's collection. {TM: Probably snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.22,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NNow if you would please sign here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 10,0:09:52.61,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that means Kaiser Loan\N has ties with that bank. {TM: with "nn"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that means Kaiser Loan\N has ties with that bank.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say Kaiser Loan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard of them, Hifumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.74,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, they're the loan sharks run by \N the infamous Kaiser Corporation, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they dirty?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.77,0:10:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiser Group is a conglomerate known \N for cleverly skirting the border of legality.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.35,0:10:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely doesn't sound like the \N cleanest place to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you borrow money from Kaiser Loan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, it's a long story.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why they only accepted cash payments.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have been trying to avoid \N leaving a paper trail.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.87,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the money \Nwas going to a bank for criminals...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.25,0:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean our money has been funding \N criminal activity this whole time?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We don't know that for sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.17,0:10:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any proof that Kaiser Loan \N was taking our money to the Black Market's bank.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.18,0:10:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but they have to issue a receipt \N when they bring the money in, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could find a record of that, \N wouldn't that serve as evidence?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.85,0:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! \N But now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.02,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the papers would already be inside the bank, \N so there's no way to get to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking inside of a bank that has \N top of the line security,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.20,0:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,even by Black Market standards, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.57,0:11:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino.\N I think this calls for that plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.45,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Which plan? Oh, right, that plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.56,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. That plan might be just what we need!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't mean THAT plan...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell me you mean THAT plan...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry, I'm not sure I...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing left to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're robbing that bank. \NExcuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, hold on! \NThere's gotta be another -
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.65,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. \NWe're just finding evidence of their crimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose that's true...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.49,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I doubt you'd listen\N even if I said no, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.54,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, what's... \N Sorry, Hifumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think far enough ahead,\N so I don't have a mask for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.84,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm doing this too?! \N We couldn't just leave you
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,out in the cold like that.\N Oh, no, no,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.72,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind at all.\NHere, Hifumi, this one's for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? \NWait, hold on, let's talk about this,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nono- hnggfh {I smell a chance for subtle shenanigans here --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.48,0:12:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks so cute on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Does this mean that
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.99,0:12:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also coming along with you, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.99,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Hifumi. \N You promised, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That you'll help us find what we're looking for.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.54,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to tell everyone \Non the student council...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine! \NWe're the good guys here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.17,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Teacher?\NI'm in, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.18,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't overlook the possibility that your money \N is being used for evil purposes, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.39,0:12:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. \NAll right, then, Masked Swimsuit Gang,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll out!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in fact I'm almost quite out of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.84,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the bottom line? \N I need money, and I need it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.47,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, but we are\N unable to process your request this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.64,0:13:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? \NYou mean you can't lend us the money?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.52,0:13:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.\N But hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an entire office! \NWhat's the issue?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your office is a rental.\NThe only hard assets you own
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.15,0:13:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,are firearms. We couldn't possibly \Nlend you any money like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?!\NIf you had something you could put up as collateral,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you had a strong credit history with us,\Nwe could lend you money,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.66,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but might I suggest you start by
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.00,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,finding a day job?\N Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,《This little jerk...\NI'm tempted to just
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.84,0:13:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,burn this place down\Nand walk out with the money.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.01,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that wouldn't work.\NThe Market Guard is here, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.39,0:14:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd never get away.\NI don't have the guts to
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.14,0:14:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,make an enemy of the Black Market.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.52,0:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,God, what am I even doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.69,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised myself I would become \Nthe number one outlaw in all of Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.53,0:14:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at me now, agonizing over\N stupid things like bank loans...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.41,0:14:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what I wanted to be doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.83,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become someone who \N lived fearlessly, by my own rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A hard-boiled outlaw...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at least, that was the dream...》
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.81,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, drop your weapons\N and get down on the ground!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.19,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bank robbers?!\NDo as we say,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or prepare to get hurt!\NUh, umm, I'd hate for anyone
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.82,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to get hurt, so stay calm, \N and get down on the ground, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wise guy. \NShe said drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, girls...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do make sure not to harm any of the civilians, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.25,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. \N Right-o. So far, so good.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to phase 2, shall we?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Faust, you're the leader. \NGive us the word!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.39,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what? \NYou mean me? I'm Faust?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NHifumi-
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.98,0:15:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Faust, you're the leader!\NIn other words, you're our boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.02,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And while we're at it,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,call me Christina, doll!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.86,0:15:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't those the girls from Abydos...?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Should we beat them up?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, looks like they're not here for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That cash transport just now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.83,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.\NI'll give you whatever you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullion, cash, bonds, anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.51,0:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that. We just want the receipts...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.68,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,《Whoa... who are these people?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hitting a bank in the Black Market of all places!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making it look so easy, too.\N So... professional!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just so cool! \NI can't get enough of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the picture definition of outlaw! {Very repetitive, but she's gushing, so I think it works? --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, I think I'm going to cry!》
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.86,0:16:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here it is!\NPlease, just take it... don't kill me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro-, sorry, Blue 2.\NDo you have the package?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, yeah. It's just...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty. Let's make like a tree and skedaddle!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.16,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we're leaving!\N Adios!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.17,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't look like \Nanyone got hurt, so... Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A-After them!\NSeal off the perimeter!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.34,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call an outlaw!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.40,0:16:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out of the hot zone.\NGood work, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.94,0:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah! We did it!\N I feel my actions
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.15,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as a teacher are questionable at best...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, you got the receipts?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.70,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! \N Just look at all that!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, did you just steal money after all?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.83,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NThe documents we need are right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowza. There's easily 100 million in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! Let's bring it back with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.13,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, wait!\NWhat? This will be a huge help for...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.18,0:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that, Serika!\NWhy the heck not?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.10,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all the money we poured \N our sweat and tears into earning!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was all going to that bank run by criminals!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.86,0:17:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,True, if we hadn't done anything, it's possible that this money
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.15,0:17:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,would have been turned into \Nweapons for criminals to use.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.36,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. What's wrong with stealing from criminals?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with Serika.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.37,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's money that was funding criminal activity.\N It'd be better if we used it for good instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.17,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, this much money would \N go a huge way towards paying off the school's debt!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.06,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with doing it like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Shiroko?\NYou already know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd say no.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.19,0:18:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Got me there, Shiroko.\NYou're exactly right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need is the papers.\NNot the money.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If we say it's okay this one time\N because it's dirty money,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens next time? \NWhat about the time after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.49,0:18:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if we let ourselves get used to this,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just keep making excuses to \N do things that we shouldn't
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.83,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,every time we get into trouble.\N And this old man just couldn't
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.50,0:18:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,bear the thought of all you young ones \N going astray like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.88,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if we were going to do something like that,\NI would have just used
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that fancy schmancy gold card \Nthat Nonomi has from the get-go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said that\Nyou didn't want to...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.89,0:18:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I remember now!\NIf we can't pay back
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the money the right way,\Nwe'll lose the Abydos we were
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to protect anyway.\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.32,0:19:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's only take the papers that we need.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?\NYes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I know what you're going through,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but holding onto this money \N might cause problems down the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.99,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's caused its fair share \N of problems already.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.67,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.55,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, don't worry!\NI'm not your enemy!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing here?\NDo we shoot her?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.30,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not beat up someone who\N just said she's not our enemy...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?\NYes, we've happened to bump into her before.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.73,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I saw the attack you pulled off earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.65,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in and out in minutes. \N It was amazing to watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such an amazing\N example of true outlaws.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.32,0:19:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I was blown away.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.28,0:19:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To witness such a daring display! \NI was shaken to my core!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.99,0:19:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've inspired me!\NI'm going to do my best to become
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.91,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,become an outlaw just like you!\N Living by my own rules,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a truly free spirit that answers to nobody!\NWhat is she talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.\NWell, there you have it, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.71,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't mind...\Ncan I ask what your name is?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our name...?\NYou know, like your group name,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.22,0:20:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or your team name? \NSomething I can use to remember
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,your brave exploits today by.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! I completely understand\Nwhat you mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Nonomi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.02,0:20:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,People call us...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Masked Swimsuit Gang?!\NWh-whoa... that's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.82,0:20:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Masked Swimsuit Gang?!\NWh-whoa... that's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just too cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, ho, ho, and once more, ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye. \N A tooth for a tooth.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.46,0:20:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We tread a path that none may follow,\Nand we do so without mercy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.17,0:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our motto!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.17,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So... cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are they up to over there...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you've had your fun.\NLet's just get out of here already.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.06,0:21:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, adios for now!\NOff we go, galloping into the sunset!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.69,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still the middle of the afternoon...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"We tread a path that none may follow..."
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember those words for as long as I live!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.99,0:21:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up now!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.49,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So when do we tell her?\NThis is hilarious, so not until way later.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so, what about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.33,0:21:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they forget to take it with them?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.01,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!\NOooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean we don't have to skip meals anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.35,0:21:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"We tread a path that none may follow..."
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.31,0:21:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write it down\N and hang it up somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.19,0:21:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Aru's been talking about\Nthe Masked Swimsuit Gang ever since we got back.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when she'll connect the dots...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.53,0:21:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the Masked Swimsuit Gang?\NThey're just the kids from Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.87,0:22:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NW-W-W-W-What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.50,0:22:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at her!\NShe's in shock!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{=3}No... no way...!

